## üöÄ Final Goal:

Deploy full-scale MERN stack application on AWS with automated CI/CD pipelines using Docker, Jenkins, GitHub Actions, Infrastructure as Code, and monitoring dashboards.

**"Learn. Build. Automate. Deploy."**
